is the group of aquatic mammals that include whales, dolphins and porpoises.

00:01:59.218 --> 00:02:04.958
In fact, Cetaceans are made up of lots of different species, 89 to be precise,

00:02:05.298 --> 00:02:11.928
and these are broadly split into two groups - the toothed whales, which

